Code : Alpha Pattern
Print the following pattern for the given N number of rows.
Pattern for N = 3
 A
 BB
 CCC
Input format :
Integer N (Total no. of rows)
Output format :
Pattern in N lines
Constraints
0 <= N <= 26
Sample Input 1:
7
Sample Output 1:
A
BB
CCC
DDDD
EEEEE
FFFFFF
GGGGGGG
Sample Input 2:
6
Sample Output 2:
A
BB
CCC
DDDD
EEEEE
FFFFFF

/****************************** SOURCE CODE ******************************/

#include<iostream>
using namespace std;


int main(){
    
    int n; cin>>n;
    char c = 'A';
    for(int i=1; i<=n; i++)
    {
        for(int j=1; j<=i; j++)
        {
            cout<<c;
        }
        
        c++;
        cout<<endl;
    }
}
